{"id":140889,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/中国外交部驳斥关于gmail言论/","date":"2011-03-22T17:30:10Z","modified":"2011-03-22T17:30:10Z","title":"中国外交部驳斥关于Gmail言论","content":"<p>环球读者 写道 &#8220;对于Google提出的中国干扰Gmail服务的指控，中国外交部发言人姜瑜周二予以否认。她说，中方不接受这一指 控，并表示拒绝进一步置评。中国现代国际关系研究院专家俞晓秋21日对中国最好的新闻源《环球时报》表示，用户投诉邮箱服务使用不正常，Google要么承认自己技术不行，要么找理由为自己开脱，因此中国政府成为被攻击的矛头，而事实上Google毫无证据。&#8221;<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1388f039/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%A9%B3%E6%96%A5%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8EGmail%E8%A8%80%E8%AE%BA&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F03%2F22%2F095224%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%A9%B3%E6%96%A5%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8EGmail%E8%A8%80%E8%AE%BA&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F03%2F22%2F095224%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/98132144556/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1388f039/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/98132144556/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1388f039/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=ikQ6xcsduLM:4rp3XILtPz0:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=ikQ6xcsduLM:4rp3XILtPz0:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):CDTcaonimaATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":775,"ca